    "uen": "201025665Z",
    "description": "<p>SERMAX being a reputable and reliable industrial product distributor strives to add business values to the product and component supplies that we offer to our customers. The products that we represent revolve around the Gases System, Gases Handling Component &amp; Equipment, Gases Distribution and Cryogenic Liquid Application. Majority of our customers are from the Industrial Gases, Cryogenic Application, Semiconductor &amp; Solar, Oil &amp; Gas and LNG sectors.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>SERMAX services the demand for expertise in Process Automation &amp; Process Control System, Instrumentation and Engineering. Our expertise and wide array of experiences can be put into use in almost any Process Automation &amp; Process Control System that is common in Industrial Gases, Semiconductor, Chemical, Petrochemical, Palm Oil, Rubber Industries, Dairy Processing, Pharmaceutical, Biotech, Water, Waste Water, CMS and Power Industries.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We offer a wide range of products suitable for small and medium sized “turnkey” projects, from initial feasibility/definition studies to maintenance and support.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We pride ourselves in providing excellent products to our customers that meets their specific needs, exceeding expectation while maintaining globally competitive pricing.<br>\n&nbsp;</p>",
